                        1. dampak positif<br />a.Children and teens can learn to develop the technical skills <br />b.Expanding network of friends, children and adolescents will be more easy to make friends with others around the world <br />c.Children and adolescents are motivated to learn to develop themselves through friends they met online <br />d.Social networking sites to make children and teenagers become more friendly, caring, and empathy<br /><br />dampak negatif<br />1.Children and teens become lazy to learn to communicate in the real world.<br />2.Social networking sites will make children and adolescents more selfish.<br />3.For children and adolescents, there are no rules of spelling and grammar in social networking.<br />maaf baru nomor 1<br /><br />
